    <abstract>
      <t>This document discusses the considerations for assigning new DiffServ Code Points (DCSPs). It considers the common remarking behaviours that the Diffserv field might be subjected to along an Internet path. It also notes some implications of using a specific DSCP. This individual draft aims to seek comments and contributions from the TSVWG working group.</t>
